{"tid":746141,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【內地多間網貸平台接連倒閉】 【永利寶清盤:行業已名存實亡","createTime":"2018-07-17T10:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T10:51:10.000Z","uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a032316b4163197917b8ad8f745e8d2ea2858681","tid":746141,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:36:35.000Z","msg":"內地再有網貸平台清盤，6 月至今已有逾百間網貸平台出現問題及停業。<br />\n<br />\n營運近五年的上海網貸平台永利寶，凌晨在公司網頁發出公告，稱因營運成本及投資者信心問題，宣布清盤退出。<br />\n<br />\n更直指網貸行業風雲突變，整個行業已名存實亡。<br />\n<br />\n內地網貸行業發展不足十年，在三年前高峰時期，全國一度有逾 4,000 間網貸平台。<br />\n<br />\n但據彭博統計，到去年第四季，減少至不足 2,000 間。上月倒閉情況更加劇，單是今個月首兩星期，已有近 50 間家平台出現問題。<br />\n<br />\n彭博報道，內地政府過去兩年，大力打擊高風險影子銀行，收緊信貸市場，對行業造成衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n業界普遍預料，市場流動性持續緊張，加上當局維持對網貸平台監管下，這一輪網貸平台倒閉潮可能會進一步加劇。"},{"pid":"bc6053b0e5bbc4d94274bb4bffee89c6d0a65126","tid":746141,"uid":159794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:38:38.000Z","msg":"咁本身借左果d <br />\n<br />\n係咪唔洗還？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ed148974b84eee0edae8c91b54bbd7d51b4726","tid":746141,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc6053b0e5bbc4d94274bb4bffee89c6d0a65126","tid":746141,"uid":159794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:38:38.000Z","msg":"咁本身借左果d <br />\n<br />\n係咪唔洗還？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:46:35.000Z","msg":"走哂人啦"},{"pid":"55a650d5464f202d749581c1798cef714a44cb15","tid":746141,"uid":23468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc6053b0e5bbc4d94274bb4bffee89c6d0a65126","tid":746141,"uid":159794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:38:38.000Z","msg":"咁本身借左果d <br />\n<br />\n係咪唔洗還？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:51:10.000Z","msg":"本來d人就係唔還，佢地先倒閉哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}